Privacy Policy for "Hello Doctor" App

At "Hello Doctor", we are committed to protecting the privacy and security of our users. This privacy policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information.

Information Collection
We collect certain personal information from you, such as your name, email address, and contact details, when you create an account or book an appointment. We may also collect information about your device and usage of the app.

Use of Information
We use your personal information to provide you with the services of the "Hello Doctor" app, including scheduling appointments, communicating with doctors, and improving our app. We do not share your information with any third parties without your consent.

Data Security
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse. Your information is stored securely and accessed only by authorized personnel.

Your Rights
You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information at any time. You can also opt-out of receiving marketing communications from us.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us at info@addisway.com
